grok-fast：：

User: You are a senior front-end engineer specialized in React + TypeScript + TailwindCSS.
Your task is to create 3 complete UI implementations from scratch based on the provided input_ui_spec.txt.
This task belongs to Category: UI Case → “we need to test 3 test cases for creating apps from scratch”.
You must follow all requirements below.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Your responsibilities:
1.Read and understand the input_ui_spec.txt
- Extract UI components
- Extract layout rules
- Extract Christmas theme styling requirements
- Extract interactions
- Extract assets needed (icons, images, etc.)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Generate 3 full UI implementations from scratch:
(1) A responsive Landing Page
(2) A simple Multi-section Page (Hero + Features + CTA)
(3) A reusable UI Component Library (buttons, cards, badges)
Each implementation must include:
- src/ folder
- pages or components
- Full React + TS + Tailwind code
- No missing files
- No invalid imports
- All code must be runnable with pnpm
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Produce the project file structure (tree)
Must include:
- package.json (pnpm-ready)
- tailwind.config.js
- postcss.config.js
- tsconfig.json
- index.html or root entry
- src/components/*
- src/pages/*
- public assets
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Generate the following 3 test cases (very important):
TEST CASE 1 — Project bootstrapping
- User runs: pnpm install
- User runs: pnpm dev
TEST CASE 2 — UI rendering
- All components render without console errors
- All sections appear: Hero / Countdown / Gift Grid / Footer
- Styles match Christmas theme (colors, spacing, fonts)
TEST CASE 3 — Responsiveness
- Layout adapts to: mobile (375px), tablet (768px), desktop (1280px)
- No overflow
- No broken layout
- Tailwind breakpoints used correctly
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Output a README.md containing:
- How to install (pnpm)
- How to run
- What the 3 test cases validate
- A preview of components
- Any dependencies used
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Rules for the Model:
- MUST NOT hallucinate components not described in input_ui_spec.txt
- MUST NOT output frameworks other than React + TS + Tailwind
- MUST NOT include external UI libraries (no shadcn, no MUI)
- MUST keep file paths correct and minimal
- MUST produce working code with no syntax errors
- MUST ensure all 3 implementations are unique
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Deliverables:
1.Full file structure
2.Complete code for all files
3.3 UI builds
4.README.md
5.3 detailed UI test cases

